---
title: Spicy Pork and Peanut Dragon Noodles with Peppers and Bok Choy
description: Fire it up! This dish is made for fans of big flavours. Peanut butter adds depth to these dragon noodles, while bell pepper and bok choy add crunch! Spicy mayo  is optional, but highly recommended for a spicy finishing drizzle!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/nouilles-du-dragon-au-porc-epice-et-aux-arachides-794c44cd.jpg
